<font size="5"><li>Install The Homebrew Channel (HBC) and Bootmii</li></font><br>
If your Wii was previously modified, and it has either the HBC, Bootmii boot2 or a Forwarder Channel installed, you can use one of those instead of an exploit in order to update the HBC and Bootmii. If you don't have these, or don't know what they are, it's okay, they aren't necessary and you'll have installed all or some of these by the end of this guide.<br>
<br>


