If this is truly your first time modding your Wii, please continue with this step to launch an exploit. An exploit is a vulnerability in the console's software that gives us access to launch the tools we'll need to complete this guide. Most Wii exploits load SD:/boot.elf or SD:/boot.dol which takes over further loading of homebrew.<br>
